\subsubsection{Money or Passion -- Life Decisions}

\begin{wrapfigure}{r}{0.3\textwidth}
	\begin{center}
		\includegraphics[width=0.28\textwidth]{financial_seal_thumb.jpg}
	\end{center}
\end{wrapfigure}

As a high school student slowly moving into maturity, it is important
for me and others to start to consider our life choices regarding financial
security. In order to make the right choices, one must first understand
some important definitions and facts. First of all one one needs to understand
the definition of financial security. Financial security is the state of
controlling one's monetary conditions. For example, one should avoid/keep track
of one's credit card and bank account informations. It is also important to
split one's wealth in smart investments, business and bank account. It is also
a good idea to start planning out one's life as early as possible. As a high
schooler, I am planning out my life, with possible college spending, work study, etc.

For example, when purchasing a video game, it is important to not only act on
interest, but one should also consider one's economic condition and other things as
well.

