\subsubsection{Educate the next generation}

Similar to what happens in many other fields, the younger generation
approaches the matter of financial security with a "I'll handle it when
it comes up." However, in the financial world, some things are too serious
to risk. For example, a credit trap is potentially fatal to one's financial
career.

